    <title>Java的几种数据类型</title>
    <link href="/2022/08/18/java%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B/"/>
    <url>/2022/08/18/java%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="几种数据类型"><a href="#几种数据类型" class="headerlink" title="几种数据类型"></a>几种数据类型</h1><h3 id="java-是强类型语言，变量使用要严格符合规定，先定义再使用"><a href="#java-是强类型语言，变量使用要严格符合规定，先定义再使用" class="headerlink" title="java 是强类型语言，变量使用要严格符合规定，先定义再使用"></a>java 是强类型语言，变量使用要严格符合规定，先定义再使用</h3><table><thead><tr><th align="center">数据类型名称</th><th align="center">占用字节</th><th>默认值</th><th>封装器类</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">byte</td><td align="center">1</td><td>0</td><td>Byte</td></tr><tr><td align="center">short</td><td align="center">2</td><td>0</td><td>Short</td></tr><tr><td align="center">int</td><td align="center">4</td><td>0</td><td>Integer</td></tr><tr><td align="center">long</td><td align="center">8</td><td>0.0l</td><td>Long</td></tr><tr><td align="center">float</td><td align="center">4</td><td>0.0f</td><td>Float</td></tr><tr><td align="center">double</td><td align="center">8</td><td>0</td><td>Double</td></tr><tr><td align="center">char</td><td align="center">2</td><td>\u0000</td><td>Character</td></tr><tr><td align="center">boolean</td><td align="center">2</td><td>false</td><td>Boolean</td></tr></tbody></table><p>Ps : 这是网上找到的表格，其中 <code>封装器类</code> 是什么意思</p><h3 id="几种基本数据类型拓展"><a href="#几种基本数据类型拓展" class="headerlink" title="几种基本数据类型拓展"></a>几种基本数据类型拓展</h3><p><em><strong>整型（int）</strong></em> 类型拓展：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">DataTypes</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">//十进制、八进制、十六进制</span><br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">a</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">10</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">b</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">010</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">c</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0x10</span>;<br>        System.out.println(a);<br>        System.out.println(b);<br>        System.out.println(c);<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>浮点数（float&#x2F;double）</strong></em> 类型拓展：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Datatypes</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">float</span> <span class="hljs-variable">f</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0.1f</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">double</span> <span class="hljs-variable">d</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1.0</span>/<span class="hljs-number">10</span>;<br>System.out.println(f == d);<span class="hljs-comment">//false</span><br>        <span class="hljs-type">float</span> <span class="hljs-variable">d1</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">23131312312312313f</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">float</span> <span class="hljs-variable">d2</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> d1 + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        System.out.println(d1 == d2);<span class="hljs-comment">//true</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>最好不要使用浮点数进行比较</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>字符（char）</strong></em>类型拓展</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Datatypes</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(String[] args)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">char</span> <span class="hljs-variable">c1</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>;<br>        <br>        System.out.println(c1);<br>        System.out.println((<span class="hljs-type">int</span>)c1);<span class="hljs-comment">//强制转换成整形97</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>每个字符都代表一个整形</p><p><em><strong>布尔（boolean）</strong></em>类型拓展</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-type">boolean</span> <span class="hljs-variable">flag</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(flag == teye)&#123;&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(flag)&#123;&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//上面两种意思完全相同</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="类型转换"><a href="#类型转换" class="headerlink" title="类型转换"></a>类型转换</h3><blockquote><p>自动类型转换<br>低———————————————————-&gt;高<br>byte、short、char-&gt;int-&gt;long-&gt;float-&gt;double</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">&gt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">128</span>;<br>&gt;<span class="hljs-type">double</span> <span class="hljs-variable">b</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> i<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em>不需要任何操作</em></p></blockquote><p><em><strong>运算中，不同类型的数据先（自动）转化为同一类型然后进行运算</strong></em></p><blockquote><p>强制类型转换（高–&gt;低）</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java">&gt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">128</span>;<br>&gt;<span class="hljs-type">byte</span> <span class="hljs-variable">b</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> (<span class="hljs-type">byte</span>)i;<span class="hljs-comment">//发生溢出</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p><strong>注意点</strong></p><ul><li>不能对布尔类型进行转换</li><li>不能转换为不相干的类型</li><li>把高容量转换到低容量的时候，强制转换</li><li>转换的时候可能存在内存溢出，或者精度问题</li></ul></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
